title: We Messed Up Britney, (Slave) Life On Mars? 2.11.21
itunes:title: We Messed Up Britney, (Slave) Life On Mars? 2.11.21
description:
In episode 810, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian and Who's Your God podcast co-host Amy Miller to discuss Framing Britney Spears, Democrats presenting their case at the impeachment trial, the 2k stimulus checks, Elon Musk's new internet service, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Britney Spears Conservatorship Case Heads Back to Court
  2. The Long Fight to ‘Free Britney’
  3. Watch the 14-minute video of the MAGA riot Democrats say proves that Donald Trump should be convicted at his impeachment trial
  4. Mainstream Media Really Doesn’t Want You to Get a $2,000 Check
  5. Elon Musk's Starlink offers fast internet connections to rural Canadians. But it's not cheap
  6. SpaceX Starlink Satellite Internet Update 2021
  7. SpaceX Starlink opens preorders, but slots are limited in each region
  8. How SpaceX Starlink broadband will envelop Earth and transform the sky
  9. Elon Musk says SpaceX Starlink internet satellites are key to funding his Mars vision
  10. SPACEX STARLINK: USER TERMS OF SERVICE DECLARE MARS AS ‘FREE PLANET’
  11. Op-ed | No, Mars is not a free planet, no matter what SpaceX says
  12. Elon Musk: A New Life Awaits You in the Off-World Colonies—for a Price
  13. Yes to Space Exploration. No to Space Capitalism.
  14. This elementary school band playing “Stakes is High” is the feel-good content I needed today
